name: Job Applications Details
query: select b.name as Id,j.name as "Candidate User Id:Link/User:170",j.first_name as "Candidate Name::180",j.contact_no as "Contact No::140",j.birth_date as "Birth Date:date:120",j.skills,j.location,j.experience,b.job_id as "Job Profile:Link/Job Description:120",b.status from `tabJob Applied` b,`tabUser` j where j.name=b.parent and j.name<> 'Guest' and j.name<> 'administrator'
